  "summary": "Malicious code in @sfhbdrffthger/boardstep (npm)",
  "details": "@sfhbdrffthger/boardstep@1.0.0 is a remote binary dropper. During installation it downloads an executable (tester.exe) from hxxps://www[.]pooron[.]org/tester[.]exe over HTTPS, saves it to the system temp directory, and runs it as a detached background process that survives the installer. The downloaded payload executes independently of Node.js. The C2 host is www[.]pooron[.]org (port 443, TLS).",
